"{\"uid\": \"jang.com.pk-en-17827-arshad-nadeem-sets-sights-on-pakistans-first-ever-olympic-gold-news\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Arshad Nadeem is eager and hopeful to win the historic Olympic gold medal for Pakistan in the javelin throw on Thursday, August 8 night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 86, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.999230054965956, \"rank\": 0.0007651522624719377, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toGeo Super, the top 12 javelin throwers in the world will compete for the Olympic medal at 11:25 pm (PST) at Sadia De France.\", \"from\": 138, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\", \"score\": 0.9962852367906424, \"rank\": 0.003280674451795889, \"text\": \"PST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Time_Zone\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadia\", \"score\": 0.9464994328250518, \"rank\": 0.056524666139819386, \"text\": \"Sadia\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadia\"}, {\"begin\": 267, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.5120136015925489, \"rank\": 0.685112285535293, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All Pakistanis are eagerly waiting to find out whether Nadeem will succeed in winning the gold glory for Pakistan after 32 years or not.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 280, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistanis\", \"score\": 0.9999878804126194, \"rank\": 1.2115464306110495e-05, \"text\": \"Pakistanis\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistanis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistanis\"}, {\"begin\": 381, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.999230054965956, \"rank\": 0.0007651522624719377, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Nadeem is optimistic about better results in the finals.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In an exclusive interview withThe News,he said, \\\"I am feeling much fitter, and I am in good rhythm this time around.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All I need is prayers from the entire nation so that I should be in a position to make my best efforts.\\\"\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He further added, \\\"A few months back I was struggling with injuries.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dengue hit me hard almost three months back.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was feeling so exhausted and weak that I had lost all hopes of even competing in the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But things got better with the passage of time\\u2026 Now I feel ready to give my best.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All I need is the nation's prayers and best wishes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem noted, \\\"We have nothing to cheer about when it comes to Olympic achievements during the last 32 years.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to end the drought and bring smiles to the faces of all those who want me to excel.\\\"\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, Nadeem will be the fourth thrower in the finals on Thursday evening.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is among a few javelin throwers who have crossed the 90-meter mark.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.Daily Jang,All Rights Reserved |Writers|Contact Us|Privacy Policy\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": []}]}"